<div class="page-title">
  <h3>Getting Started</h3>	
</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">

<div class="grid-simple">
  <div class="grid-body no-border">
    <ol>
      <li>
        <h4>Create account.</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/register" target="_blank"><strong>Create an Account</strong></a>, or login if you already have account.</li>
          <li><a href="/account/workers" target="_blank"><strong>Add a Worker</strong></a> that will be used by the mining app to login.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h4>Download a Mining App</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://ck.kolivas.org/apps/cgminer/" target="_blank"><strong>CGMiner</strong></a> <em>Windows/Linux</em></li>
          <li><a href="http://www.asteroidapp.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Asteroid</strong></a> <em>Mac OSX</em> </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h4>Configure Your Miner</h4>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 m-b-20">
            <div class="stratum-info">
              <h4>USA: stratum+tcp://us-west.nimblecoin.us:3333 -u username.workername -p nimblecoin</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 m-b-20">
            <div class="stratum-info">
              <h4>USA: stratum+tcp://us-east.nimblecoin.us:3333 -u username.workername -p nimblecoin</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="stratum-info">
              <h4>EU: stratum+tcp://uk.nimblecoin.us:3333 -u username.workername -p nimblecoin</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h4>Set Up Your Wallet</h4>
         <ul>
            <li><a href="http://www.dogecoin.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Download the Dogecoin Wallet App</strong></a>.</li>
            <li>Generate a new address and set it as your <strong>Payout Address</strong> in <a href="/account/edit" target="_blank"><strong>Account Settings</strong></a>.</li>
          </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h4>Join the Community!</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=nimblecoin" target="_blank"><strong>#nimblecoin</strong> on Freenode</a> — IRC Chat with Friendly Admins.</li>
          <li><a href="http://reddit.com/r/dogecoin" target="_blank"><strong>/r/dogecoin</strong></a> — All things Doge.</li>
          <li><a href="http://reddit.com/r/dogemining" target="_blank"><strong>/r/dogemining</strong></a> — For mining related help.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
